            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </li>
      
      <li class="ctsh clearfix" data-cid="19359037">
        <div class="ilst">
          <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/newray/"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u62517499-2.jpg" alt="牛石头" class="" /></a>
        </div>
        <div class="con">
          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
